name: Rounding the Fastnet
description: To mark the company’s 10 year anniversary, Keeper Solutions Founder Stephen Walsh collaborated with Irish artist Tom Moore, known in the art world as Cereal Tom (www.cerealtom.com). ‘Rounding the Fastnet’ was inspired by vintage tourism posters and depicts a sailboat rounding the iconic Fastnet Rock, a lighthouse located off the coast of Cork, Ireland. The music featured in the piece is an excerpt from Chopin’s Ballade No.1 sourced on musicopen.com -> here is the attribution link https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Frederic_Chopin_-_ballade_no._1_in_g_minor,_op._23.ogg
